{"type":null,"faqId":9531,"title":"P6S-U06  蓝牙与电脑连接上网，蓝牙传输文件","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">支持与电脑共享网络，支持蓝牙游戏。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">手机支持</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">PAN</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">Personal\nArea Network Profile</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">），支持其他设备共享手机的网络资源。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">在<b>设置</b></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> -&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">更多</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">...</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> -&gt;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">网络共享与便携式热点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">中，勾选蓝牙共享网络；接受对方发起的连接后，即可建立自己的个人局域网络。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29974\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29975\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">手机支持蓝牙游戏。此功能更多取决于三方应用的设计，一般的步骤为：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>a)<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">在游戏中选择搜索其他蓝牙设备。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>b)<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">找到你连接的蓝牙设备预置配对</span><span>OK</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>c)<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">开始游戏。</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"></span> \n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":13